text: Hannah Dodd (born 17 May 1995) is an English actress, dancer and model. Her first well known role was in the Hulu teen series Find Me in Paris (2018–2020). She is best known for her role as Francesco Bridgerton in the Netflix serious Bridgerton (2024–). Dodd was born in Colchester and grew up in Leavenheath on the Essex–Suffolk border.
